    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，准确说是thread.start(FinTech_PaymentGateway)，因为支付网关是实际执行业务的组件。这里需要把RUNNABLE和RUNNING放在一个子图里，叫Thread Scheduler。",
      "elements_involved": [
