        "Thread Scheduler",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，子图已添加。现在RUNNABLE到RUNNING的转换条件是CPU时间分配，这个我理解。但RUNNING回到RUNNABLE的情况需要确认一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
