    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "正确，获取到锁之后退出synchronized块就回到RUNNABLE。接下来还有WAITING状态，这是调用object.wait()时进入的，具体是在FinTech_TransactionQueue上等待。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING",
